data.title: Community Grants
data.meta_description: Oracle supports nonprofit organizations that provide health and human services, assist people in need, and strengthen the infrastructure that supports a healthy society.
data.text:
“During the pandemic, we saw a 220% increase in families turning to the Food Bank for the first time. We’re thankful to Oracle for standing by our side to help feed our most vulnerable neighbors and families who never imagined they would need a helping hand.”

Mark Jackson Chief Development Officer, Central Texas Food Bank
